Introduction

Kriesha Chu (크리샤 츄) is a Filipino-American-Chinese singer under New Way Company. She is best known for being a contestant in the competition show K-Pop Star 6 and finished as a runner-up (as KWINs). She made her solo debut on May 24, 2017 with the single album "Kriesha Chu 1st Single Album".
